        <div class="col s12 m4">
          <div class="icon-block">
            <h2 class="center light-blue-text"><i class="material-icons">flash_on</i></h2>
            <h5 class="center">Streamlined</h5>

            <p class="light">WAHA loosely couples components to simplify integration with existing enterprise identity
              systems and administrative appliance portals using available protocols and standards.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col s12 m4">
          <div class="icon-block">
            <h2 class="center light-blue-text"><i class="material-icons">group</i></h2>
            <h5 class="center">Centralized</h5>

            <p class="light">Appliances using this centralized MFA enabling service will no longer require independent
              administration. Leveraging centralized directory services will enable Role Based (group based) entitlement
              assignments.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col s12 m4">
          <div class="icon-block">
            <h2 class="center light-blue-text"><i class="material-icons">settings</i></h2>
            <h5 class="center">Automated</h5>

            <p class="light">Enterprise account management (IAM) processes such as periodic ID Certification and
              detailed auditing of rights assignments can be streamlined and automated.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
    <br><br>
